Rating: 4
Delicious! ...although quite time consuming. My husband asks for this dish all the time. I agree with the reviewer who thought it was too soupy; you didn't misread, it asks for one cup of coconut milk and 1/4 cup dessicated coconut. Next time I'll reduce the coconut milk and try serving it in lettuce leaves.

